Pao de Acucar’s Diniz May Seek to Buy Casino’s Stake, Valor Says

-- B y   F r a n c i s c o   M a r c e l i n o
-- 
2011-07-07T11:31:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/pao-de-acucar-s-diniz-may-seek-to-buy-casino-s-stake-valor-says.html
Cia. Brasileira de Distribuicao Grupo
Pao de Acucar Chairman Abilio Diniz said he may seek to buy
 Casino Guichard-Perrachon SA (CO) ’s stake in the Brazilian retailer,
 Valor Economico  reported.  Investment funds would help in the stake purchase if Casino
doesn’t accept the proposed merger of Pao de Acucar with
 Carrefour SA (CA) ’s unit in  Brazil , Diniz told the Sao Paulo-based
newspaper in an interview.  Diniz and Casino share control of Pao de Acucar.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francisco Marcelino in New York at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
